ChemblBioactivity - Class in uk.ac.ebi.ep.adapter.chembl
Bioactivity of a compound against a target, as measured by the number of assays and how many of them are functional and the degree of confidence.
See CONFIDENCE_SCORE_LOOKUP and ASSAY_TYPE tables in ChEMBL database.
